name: Sweet Swallows Deep V-Neck Burnout in Washed Black with Periwinkle Blue Screenprint
description:
This is an adorable design of two sweet swallows in flight with a floral, swirly pattern extending from the wings. 

This original design is screen printed by hand with love by me with periwinkle ink on a Large washed black burnout v-neck tee. 

This long cut, deep v-neck burnout tee has a supsersoft vintage feel. These shirts run a size small, and they are semi-sheer, so you might want to wear a tank underneath. They are a very soft, stretchy material.

These sizes run a size small, so this is really a Medium.

Convo me with any questions! Thanks! (See profile for sizing info.)

This fabric is put through an extensive process showing years of weathering; each bit of pilling and striation in this sheer fabric captures true vintage worn-in feel. Every tee is a unique piece. Matching self fabric cuffs. Garment dyed/washed. No shrinkage. Wash in cold water, dry on low heat. Or for best results - handwash. Do not iron print.

name: Haute Mama Maternity shirt in White with Hot Pink Screenprint
description:
**As Seen In: The EcoEtsy Mother's Day Gift Guide!**

This one's for all the Haute Mamas out there! Are you preggers and proud? This is the shirt for you! ;)

I created this shirt, and my “Haute Mama, Baby & Beyond” Collection to answer the need I saw while shopping when I was pregnant. I coudn’t find any clothes that showed how happy I was to be creating a little human being inside of me. I just wore regular clothes in larger sizes to fit my belly.

Maternity clothes were just plain UGLY! So, I set out to create a line that will showcase the glowing mamas with cute baby bellies, and make women feel GOOD about being pregnant. I print on only the softest, most-comfy fabrics, with longer lengths, and hip styles.

I was a glowing mama when I was preggers. I really enjoyed it. And I hope that my collection will make mamas feel as pretty and amazing as they are!!!!

*****
*Available in: M/L ONLY at this time
This is a wonderfully soft size Medium/Large,and fits like a Medium. I can order different sizes. Convo me!

***

"For you created my inmost being; you knit me together in my mother's womb. I praise you because I am fearfully and wonderfully made..." ~Psalm 139:13-14a
